#: src/qml/pages/Discover.qml:21
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt ""
"@info:usagetip %1 is 'Discover', the name of KDE's software center app"
msgid ""
"The <application>%1</application> app helps you find and install "
"applications, games, and tools. You can search or browse by category, look "
"at screenshots, and read reviews to help you find the perfect app."
msgstr ""
"A aplicación <application>%1</application> axúdalle a atopar e instalar "
"aplicacións, xogos e ferramentas. Pode buscar ou explorar por categoría, "
"ollar capturas de pantalla e ler recensións como axuda para atopar a "
"aplicación perfecta."

#: src/qml/pages/Discover.qml:105
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button %1 is the name of an app"
msgid "Show %1 in Discover"
msgstr "Amosar %1 en Discover"

#: src/qml/pages/Enjoy.qml:19
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:window"
msgid "Enjoy It!"
msgstr "Góceo!"

#: src/qml/pages/Enjoy.qml:20
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"We hope you love Plasma as much as we loved making it for you! Now it’s time "
"to jump right in. Explore its features, install your favorite apps and "
"games, and get busy doing what makes you you!"
msgstr ""
"Esperamos que Plasma lle guste tanto como a nós facelo para vostede! Agora "
"toca usalo. Explore as súas funcionalidades, instale as súas aplicacións e "
"xogos favoritos, e faga todo o que queira!"

#: src/qml/pages/Enjoy.qml:25
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:URL"
msgid "Learn more about the KDE community"
msgstr "Informarse sobre a comunidade KDE"

#: src/qml/pages/Enjoy.qml:30
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:URL"
msgid "Get help at KDE’s discussion forums"
msgstr "Obter axuda nos foros de discusión de KDE"

#: src/qml/pages/Enjoy.qml:60
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"If you find Plasma to be useful, consider getting involved or donating. KDE "
"is an international volunteer community, not a big company; your "
"contributions make a real difference!"
msgstr ""
"Se Plasma lle resulta útil, considere colaborar ou doar. KDE é unha "
"comunidade de voluntariado internacional, non unha gran empresa; son as súas "
"contribucións as que cambian as cousas."

