#: src/qml/pages/Network.qml:19
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:window"
msgid "Access the Internet"
msgstr "Acceso a Internet"

#: src/qml/pages/Network.qml:20
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"You can connect to the internet and manage your network connections with the "
"<interface>Networks applet</interface>. To access it, click on the "
"<interface>Networks</interface> icon in your <interface>System Tray</"
"interface>, which lives in the bottom-right corner of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Pode conectarse a Internet e xestionar as súas conexións de rede coa "
"<interface>miniaplicación de redes</interface>. Para acceder a el, prema a "
"icona de <interface>Redes</interface> na <interface>área de notificación</"
"interface>, que está na esquina inferior dereita da pantalla."

#: src/qml/pages/Network.qml:74
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:placeholder"
msgid "Networking support for Plasma is not currently installed"
msgstr "A funcionalidade de rede de Plasma non está instalada."

#: src/qml/pages/Network.qml:75
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip %1 is the name of the user's distro"
msgid ""
"To manage network connections, Plasma requires <icode>plasma-nm</icode> to "
"be installed. Please report this omission to %1."
msgstr ""
"Plasma necesita <icode>plasma-nm</icode> instalado para xestionar conexións "
"de rede. Informe deste problema a %1."

#: src/qml/pages/Network.qml:249
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:placeholder Shown when connected to the internet"
msgid "You’re connected"
msgstr "Conectouse"

#: src/qml/pages/Network.qml:250
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip Shown when connected to the internet"
msgid "All good to go!"
msgstr "Listo!"

#: src/qml/pages/Network.qml:258
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info"
msgid ""
"This page is being shown regardless of network connectivity because you are "
"using a development version. To manually preview the different states of the "
"page, you can use the button."
msgstr ""
"Esta páxina amósase independentemente da conectividade de rede porque está a "
"usar unha versión de desenvolvemento. Use o botón para obter manualmente "
"unha vista previa dos distintos estados da páxina."

#: src/qml/pages/Network.qml:263
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "Change state"
msgstr "Cambiar o estado"

#: src/qml/pages/PlasmaUpdate.qml:17
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title:window"
msgid "Plasma has been updated to %1"
msgstr "Plasma actualizouse a %1"

#: src/qml/pages/plasmaupdate/Beta.qml:17
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"Thank you for testing this beta release of Plasma — your feedback is "
"fundamental to helping us improve it! Please report any and all bugs you "
"find so that we can fix them."
msgstr ""
"Grazas por probar esta versión de Plasma. As súas achegas son fundamentais "
"para axudarnos a melloralo! Informe de calquera fallo que atope para que "
"poidamos solucionalo."

#: src/qml/pages/plasmaupdate/Beta.qml:23
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:URL"
msgid "<b>Find out what’s new</b>"
msgstr "<b>Descubrir as novidades</b>"

#: src/qml/pages/plasmaupdate/Beta.qml:28
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:URL"
msgid "Report a bug"
msgstr "Informar dun fallo"

#: src/qml/pages/plasmaupdate/Beta.qml:32
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@label:URL"
msgid "Help work on the next release"
msgstr "Axudar coa seguinte versión"

#: src/qml/pages/plasmaupdate/Update.qml:18
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"KDE contributors have spent the last four months hard at work on this "
"release. We hope you enjoy using Plasma as much as we enjoyed making it!"
msgstr ""
"A xente de KDE leva catro meses traballando nesta versión. Esperamos que o "
"pase tan ben usándoa como nós facéndoa!"

#: src/qml/pages/plasmaupdate/Update.qml:24
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "<b>Find out what's new</b>"
msgstr "<b>Descubrir as novidades</b>"

#: src/qml/pages/plasmaupdate/Update.qml:29
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@action:button"
msgid "Help work on the next release"
msgstr "Axudar coa seguinte versión"

#: src/qml/pages/plasmaupdate/Update.qml:70
#, kde-kuit-format
msgctxt "@info:usagetip"
msgid ""
"The KDE community relies on donations of expertise and funds, and is "
"supported by KDE e.V.—a German nonprofit. Donations to KDE e.V. support the "
"wider KDE community, and you can make a difference by donating today."
msgstr ""
"A comunidade KDE depende de doazóns de experiencia e fondos, e ten o apoio "
"de KDE e.V., unha organización alemá sen ánimo de lucro. As doazóns a KDE e."
"V. apoian á comunidade KDE no seu conxunto, e vostede pode axudar doando "
"hoxe."

